@shikoo: Both netori and netorare are abbreviated as NTR. They're just different forms of the root verb NETORU: "to sleep with / take someone else's partner." ---*---*--- In general use, NETORI = netoru as a noun: "taking someone else's partner". And NETORARE = the passive form of this: "having one's partner taken". ---*---*--- In kink and porn, NETORI = the sexual fantasy of partner-taking: the netori fan gets excited when a hentai doujin's MC fucks someone else's partner... While NETORARE = the fantasy of partner-losing: the netorare fan gets excited when someone else fucks the MC's partner.
